edia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other legendary British stars took part in the glitzy ceremony, including the Spice Girls, who reunited on stage for a jaw-dropping performance, as well as George Michael and Paul McCartney.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6620242968138534, \"rank\": 0.4853853856097897, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 650, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Michael\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7900939639256645e-34, \"text\": \"George Michael\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Michael\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Michael\"}, {\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.314001841771669e-16, \"text\": \"Paul McCartney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans rushed to social media to make the brutal comparison, as one said: \\\"Danny Boyle and Graham Norton trending, just goes to show that no one puts on a show like The Irish.\\\"\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danny Boyle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\"}, {\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gra